@ApiGateway_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Gateway Info
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/gateway/info
Accept: application/json

###

### Gateway Routes
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/gateway/routes
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Correlation ID
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/gateway/info
X-Correlation-ID: test-correlation-123
Accept: application/json

###

### Register User (through Gateway)
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123!",
  "username": "testuser"
}

###

### Login (through Gateway)
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "TestPassword123!"
}

###

### Refresh Token (through Gateway)
# @name refreshToken
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh-token
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refresh_token}}"
}

###

### Protected Endpoint Test (with Bearer Token)
GET {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/protected-endpoint
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Rate Limiting
# Execute this multiple times rapidly to test rate limiting
POST {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "wrong"
}

###

### Test CORS Preflight
OPTIONS {{ApiGateway_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Origin: http://localhost:4200
Access-Control-Request-Method: POST
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Content-Type

